#Base Project Slim + Illuminate ORM + Mustache Template engine

This is the basic skeleton of an application that provide system routes, ORM and templates engine.

----------

##Tech
- **[Slim](http://www.slimframework.com/)** - The Slim is a microframework that provides a good route structure in addition to being a great way to build REST APIs
- **[Eloquent ORM](http://laravel.com/docs/4.2/eloquent)**: It is an ORM Laravel proving a good abstraction database
- **[Mustache](http://mustache.github.io/)** - The Mustache is one of the best known templates systems, it has a friendly syntax and can be used in the Back-end and Front-end

----------

##Init
Clone the project then run the composer
```
composer install
```
----------

